natspec.details: available functions: stakeTokens, unStakeTokens, issueTokens, addAllowedTokens, getValue

addAllowedTokens(address).details: only owner may call this function

getSingleTokenValue(address,address).details: converts token value to USDtoken's price * user's staking balance
getSingleTokenValue(address,address).notice: get value of each user's token

issueTokens().details: only owner may call this function
issueTokens().notice: send stakers token reward based on TVL

owner().details: Returns the address of the current owner.

renounceOwnership().details: Leaves the contract without owner. It will not be possible to call `onlyOwner` functions anymore. Can only be called by the current owner. NOTE: Renouncing ownership will leave the contract without an owner, thereby removing any functionality that is only available to the owner.

setPriceFeedContract(address,address).details: only owner may call this function
setPriceFeedContract(address,address).notice: set price feed for this contract

params._amount: how much token wanted to be staked

tokenIsAllowed(address).notice: check is token allowed to stake

transferOwnership(address).details: Transfers ownership of the contract to a new account (`newOwner`). Can only be called by the current owner.

unstakeTokens(address).notice: transfer the staked balance back to the owner
